claim.claim-text:
A mobile terminal(1 00), comprising:
a housing having a front surface, a rear surface and a lateral surface;
a display(151) at the front surface of the housing to display an object at a first location of a display area;
a sensor(231) at the lateral surface of the housing to sense a pressure being applied thereto; and
a controller(180) to change a location of the object from the first location to a second location of the display area when the sensed pressure is greater than a predetermined value.
